1.0.2   (7th April 2014)

Ctrl-K              :   "kill-line"


1.0.3   (17th April 2014)

Alt-U               :   "upcase-word"
Alt-L               :   "downcase-word"
Ctrl-G Ctrl-/       :   Redo
Ctrl-X Ctrl-W       :   "write-file"

